			<outline text="August 12" created="Thu, 12 Aug 2021 14:14:30 GMT" type="calendarDay" name="12">
				<outline text="Hit a milestone today. [[Drummer]] is working with [[Old School]]. So the best outliner now is hooked up with the best blogging CMS. Friends are trying it out now and letting me know if the software works, and if my docs work. Exciting moment. " created="Thu, 12 Aug 2021 22:10:30 GMT" type="outline"/>
