				<outline text="This could be the last Olympics." created="Fri, 06 Aug 2021 13:27:30 GMT" type="outline"/>
				<outline text="We've got a trifecta of disasters brewing now. 1. The resurgence of Covid. 2. The explosion of climate change. 3. The rot of fascism." created="Fri, 06 Aug 2021 13:27:34 GMT" type="outline"/>
				<outline text="This &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.washingtonpost.com/climate-environment/2021/08/05/change-ocean-collapse-atlantic-meridional/&quot;&gt;article&lt;/a&gt;, while shocking, doesn't explain how devastating it will be if the &lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gulf_Stream&quot;&gt;Gulf Stream&lt;/a&gt; disappears. The Gulf Stream is why &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.thesun.co.uk/news/2569640/what-is-the-gulf-stream-where-is-it-how-does-it-affect-uk-weather-and-why-does-it-cause-heavy-snow/#:~:text=How%20does%20the%20Gulf%20Stream,to%205%20%C2%B0C%20cooler.&quot;&gt;the UK&lt;/a&gt; has a temperate climate, even though it's at the same &lt;a href=&quot;https://earth.google.com/web/@46.01634833,-6.80705831,-3927.74817016a,9514760.87145209d,35y,0h,0t,0r&quot;&gt;latitude&lt;/a&gt; as &lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hudson_Bay&quot;&gt;Hudson Bay&lt;/a&gt; in Canada. " created="Fri, 06 Aug 2021 13:20:02 GMT" type="tweet" tweetId="1423637549667454996" tweetUserName="davewiner"/>
